The paper discusses the creation of a large-scale question-answer corpus using a neural network architecture, which falls under the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The evaluation metrics used in the paper also include information retrieval (cs.IR) and neural networks (cs.NE).
